https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/mem/intune/fundamentals/high-level-architecture

Intune handles MDM and MAM
    MDM - Mobile Device Management - Enforce configs and settings.
    MAM - Mobile Application Management - Applications coded to work with Intune

Integrates with O365, AAD, AIP

Can be configured as:
    100% intune
    Co-managed with Config manager

Microsoft Endpoint Manager - Co-management between SCCM and Intune
    Decide which solution is responsible for which activity.

Intune licenses bundled with a lot of other Enterprise-type licenses.
Can also do a standalone sub.
Can also do device only sub. For IOT type devices

License may let you use SCCM as well.
